{"tid":801055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：沙中綫紅磡站月台層板現「蜂巢」","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T02:03:00.000Z","uid":51620,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8962a25063189a19ccfacb9fa621da5ac56f772","tid":801055,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318666&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318666%26refer%3Dshare&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5039728a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318666%26refer%3Dshare&h=dbe5a55f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318666&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府指沙中綫紅磡站的部分月台層板，發現有混凝土剝落及鋼筋外露，已派人即時移除有問題的部分，強調安全風險已解除，結構上沒有明顯危險。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指出現蜂巢的位置約有10厘米、即4吋深，由禮頓及其分判商負責這一部分的石屎，目前正檢視相關成因。路政署又指已要求港鐵一星期內全面勘察，檢視月台層板的安全質量，並向屋宇署提交調查報告和復修方案。"},{"pid":"3c53908a7ba4165322faa73ad6e3e77b2c1a93bb","tid":801055,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c400f67d9ac46528f06a95d057ddea20855b6d","tid":801055,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"734fe54ca968d72389a7ef5ab2f233a22134cffb","tid":801055,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"混凝土剝落  補返  ＝ 冇危險？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d215e22a3d4dc0db8cc9228952b6fe3d0e005d","tid":801055,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gi